				<h1><span>Q </span>Are there any rules governing public access to surveillance video tape?</h1>

				
		</div>




		<div class="main_news_container">

			
			<div class="answer_container">
			
				<div class="answer_body">
				
								
					<img src="temp_art/mug3.jpg" class="question_avatar">
